<div class="docs-section">
  <h2 class="docs-section__title">Dark Variant</h2>
  <p class="docs-section__description">Use on dark or brand-coloured section backgrounds — hero footers, charcoal content bands, or full-bleed dark panels. The semi-transparent white icon box and inverted text ensure legibility without competing with the surrounding content. The icon itself turns white so it reads clearly against the translucent background. Use the same three-per-row grid guidance as the light variant. Avoid placing the dark variant directly beside the light variant in the same layout — choose one per section.</p>
